  "description": "A sine wave fed into maximum prism feedback and wide spread — the source material dissolves completely into a shimmering 6-facet delay cloud. Bounce gravity near 1.0: every click rebound is a ghost of the original pitch. Almost no direct signal remains. What you hear is the prism eating itself.",
